
NOTE: Change the path to your verification folder.

The script can be used as -

valid.py -option

THe options are -

1. 32       - All 32 bit tests
2. control  - All control instructions
3. data     - All data instructions
4. float    - All floating point instructions
5. integer  - All integer_alu instructions
6. misc     - Some instructions such as rd_wr,save,restore etc.
7. pipe     - Verifying pipeline
8. cache    - Cache based validation
9. Ctests   - Basic C programs 
10. memory  - Memory test with and without mmu
11. mmu     - mmu validation suite 
12. serial  - serial devide tests
13. template- C with inline assembly 
14. timer   - Testing the timer
